{"tid":1282412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉引入「確認書」制度","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T23:08:55.000Z","uid":260428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6eca6f288315eb8626d0657124ea91446242960c","tid":1282412,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"選舉管理委員會原訂今晚舉行區議會選舉活動建議指引公眾諮詢會，但經風險評估後，基於「公眾安全和保安考慮」決定取消。 <br />\n<br />\n政府的新聞稿指，選管會公眾諮詢大會，原定今晚 7 時至 9 時在鰂魚涌舉行，由於要考慮場內所有參與者的安全，經風險評估，決定取消今晚的大會。選管會建議指引的公眾諮詢，由 6 月 11 日開始，諮詢期到 7 月 10 日結束，為期三十日，當局指巿民可提供書面意見。<br />\n<br />\n選管會今次提出修改「區議會選舉活動建議指引」，其中一項修訂包括在區議會選舉引入「確認書」制度。公民黨昨日在 fb 發文，指「確認書殺入區議會選舉 DQ參選人更方便」，呼籲公眾關注今晚的諮詢會，「做個好公民，記得積極去發表意見！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選管會暫時未有提及會否改期重辦公眾諮詢大會，如就建議指引內容有書面意見，可以從三個方式表達：郵寄（香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處）、傳真（2511 1682）及電郵（eacenq@eac.hk）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無公眾諮詢<br />\n大家有無寫信格式建議"},{"pid":"69a0b227f509258635d1039b2130744c491cfc23","tid":1282412,"uid":103718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"依單野要推推"},{"pid":"b90df057ea619e90b8297596546ba2e98c71a0f2","tid":1282412,"uid":123511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:22:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb3ebcb1ec5a4e2134faea56c864b222df3455ba","tid":1282412,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f51e723f5e6c4b92e9fc9bd6c9e50bccbc16b3","tid":1282412,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"搞掂！唔該幫手推！<br />\n【全民反DQ！】一人一信反對區議會選舉DQ參選人資格！7月10號截止 ➡️ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/stopDQnow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FstopDQnow&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=a334ee1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/stopDQnow</a>"},{"pid":"e7303ef4ae31ebd90ae1b762d979ff21e8cd6496","tid":1282412,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06f51e723f5e6c4b92e9fc9bd6c9e50bccbc16b3","tid":1282412,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"搞掂！唔該幫手推！<br />\n【全民反DQ！】一人一信反對區議會選舉DQ參選人資格！7月10號截止 ➡️ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/stopDQnow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FstopDQnow&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=a334ee1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/stopDQnow</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"好掂"}]}